  "html": "<p>Protocol 33 // The Pulse<br>Initializing Link to {{1.record.name}}...</p><p>The connection is stable.</p><p>You have successfully been added to the master broadcast list. Every morning at dawn, you will receive The Pulse: a direct, unvarnished transmission decoding the energetic weather you are currently moving through.</p><p>We track the daily Nakshatra (moon transit), map the global Shadow Windows (Rahu and Yama Kaal times where you should pull back from friction), and issue a somatic command to direct your nervous system appropriately.</p><p><strong>To Ensure Delivery:</strong><br>Algorithms are sensitive to deep truth. To guarantee The Pulse arrives in your primary inbox, please reply to this email with a simple \"Secured\", and mathematically ensure pulse@mailer.p33eft.com is added to your VIP contacts list.</p><p>Your first forecast arrives tomorrow.</p><p>Navigate well.<br>Protocol 33</p>"
